description:
Only six members from Weapon X and the Exiles will be able to move on to the next world, but which six will make the cut ? The battle begins with a bloodbath ! In this fight, Weapon X and the Exiles were having a bloodish fight. First, Spider got killed by Firestar, Next Firestar, Gambit, Hulk, and all the other members were killed by Hyperion.

The Exiles tried to defeat him, but since Hyperion is to powerful, he seriously injured Morph and some other Members too. Until Blink hit him once. This isn't going to be a good battle.The story continues in the next issue.....
name: A Blink In Time (Part 2 of 3)

description: The decisive battle to see which six members survive past this world heats up as only eight members from Weapon X and the Exiles are still alive!
name: A Blink in Time (part 3 of 3)

description: "Earn Your Wings" parts 1 of 3. There's no rest for the weary when there are realities to save. After the devastating events of their last mission, the Exiles hope for a little downtime, only to find themselves 'ported directly into a none-too-friendly reception from the regular Marvel Universe. This X-Men: Reload issue is a perfect jumping-on point, featuring the debut of new writer Tony Bedard and the promotion of Exiles cover artist Mizuki Sakakibara to regular artist. Guest-starring the Fantastic Four and Beak from New-X-Men.
name: Earn Your Wings, Part 1

description:
Harvey moves to Midville High from the city because his parents want some peace and quiet. Harvey is unhappy because he doesn't want to leave his friends behind. However, he immediately gets into some hijinks and is accepted into a large, rowdy group of friends, upsetting all his parents' plans for quiet times.

Stories: "Harvey and Duke," "Harvey and Raven," "Raquel and Goober," "Here's Harvey," and "Duke."
